creator: Tacter
descriptionHtml:
Tacter is your #1 TFT app. Join thousands of users that use Tacter to win more games on Teamfight Tactics and climb the ranking ladder.

Improve your gaming experience by getting detailed compositions to play. Theorycraft by creating your own tft comps and be up to date with the last updates for free.

Thousands of players have already started climbing up on Tacter, join our community!

3 WAYS OF WINNING AT TFT WITH TACTER

• Queue up in a TFT game, choose a Tacter meta comp given your early champions and items, learn in-depth about the comp and win!

• Create your own TFT compositions and share them with your friends. Plan ahead strategies while playing the game with the composition builder, or theorycraft even if you’re not playing.

• Keep track of the rank of your friends and favourite streamer Riot Games summoners.

READ WHAT OTHER USERS THINK ABOUT TACTER

• Rank up to Platinum within a week using this app. ★★★★★
“First off what you want from this app is to help you win in TFT, right? Well for me this app definitely helped me win. I was easily able to rank up to plat within a week mostly with the help of this app. The ability to create your own comp is really user friendly and thorough. It keeps the game fun when you win games with your own comp that you designed.”
-Jeffharje.

• Best tool for quick reference vs going on a website. ★★★★★
“As a non-LoL (League of Legends) person coming for only Team fight Tactics after friends requested, this is a fantastic tool to help you learn the item and synergy mechanics. Best is you always have it as a quick reference vs taking the time mid game to go to a website. It’s beneficial to established and new players to have this app, it’s honestly fantastic.”
-MPLS_Twin.

JOIN TACTER PRO

• In-depth information about the most OP meta compositions of TFT.
• Get rid of the ads for a faster and no-distracting gaming experience.
• Support us, a lot of great stuff will be coming and we'll need your help!
